title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 – May 10 2022

description:
Kudlow on economy: Buckle up. Jim Jordan: There'd be no war in Ukraine with Trump. New WH press secretary doesn't know who's running point on baby formula shortage. Joe Manchin saves Democrats again on abortion legislation. Vivek Ramaswamy, Founder and Executive Chairman of Strive and author of Woke, Inc., joins Clay and Buck to tell us how he's pushing back on woke corporate America. Could you land a plane if the pilot was incapacitated? C&B weigh in.

Follow Clay & Buck on YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/c/clayandbuck
